B.a06=new A.aD('BUG FIXES:\n- Increased sheet update reliability\n- Improved loading transitions\n- Fixed control panel function reliability\n- Upgraded to new version of Flutter\n\nNEW FEATURES:\n- Better UI for Loading Screen and when no data is found\n- Dashboard screen with graphs for visualisation\n- Added quiz mode\n- Added leaderboard\n- Added Firebase Analytics\n- Added Control Panel Screen\n- Added mileage tracker\n- Added WPT 1 & 2 tracker\n- Google Sheets functionality for mileage tracker\n- Improved Google Sheets delete function\n- Added reset password function\n- Flashcard game\n\n\n---PAST VERSIONS---\nVersion 3.3.12\n\nBUG FIXES:\n- Resolved filter limit bug due to Firebase restrictions\n- Added refresh limit (only 1 refresh per minute)\n- Edit and Delete fault / vehicle bug in admin and moderator screens remedied\n- Fixed bug when adding fault\n\nNEW FEATURES:\n- Enhanced User Interface\n  - New MSC logo\n  - New gradient color scheme\n  - Improved bottom navigation bar UI\n- To increase user capacity, users can now only view the own faults they added, from their vehicle watchlist\n- Only admins can view all faults and vehicles\n- Realtime Google Sheets fleet status update\n- Added progress dropdown for vehicles\n- Improved list tile layout\n- Added local delete function\n\nVersion 2.3.6\n\nBUG FIXES:\n\n- Dialogues are now scrollable\n- Vehicle Details dialogue now only shows resolved faults, instead of all faults\n- Added checks and warnings for adding duplicates of vehicles\n- Added automatic refresh when new faults / vehicles are added\n- Fixed empty fault list bug\n- Bottom sheet now moves with keyboard\n\nNEW FEATURES:\n\n- Improved user interface for app drawer\n- Editing faults and vehicles made easier using scrollable bottom sheets instead of small dialogue boxes\n- Filter vehicles and faults by platoon\n- Bottom navigation for toggling fault history\n- Added slide to delete function for faults\n- Added weapon tagging for each vehicle\n- Users are now split into moderators, active users and users pending approval.\n- Admin and moderators can approve new users, suspend current users and make current users moderators via "Manage Users" screen.\n- Only admin and moderators are allowed to make announcements\n- Admin and moderators can now export and download data into excel file via settings page\n- Users screen can now filter by platoon\n\nOPTIMIZATION:\n- Reduced number of Firebase queries using Flutter Providers\n',null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null)
